<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm text-sm">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-black text-[#002b5c] uppercase mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-4">Last Updated: February 12, 2026</p>
    <h2 class="font-bold mt-4">1. Information Collection</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">Nagpur Mail ("we", "us") may collect personal information when you subscribe to our newsletter or use our contact form. This includes your name and email address.</p>
    <h2 class="font-bold mt-4">2. Cookies & Google AdSense</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">We use cookies to personalize content and ads. Third-party vendors, including Google, use cookies to serve ads based on a user's prior visits to your website or other websites.</p>
    <p class="mb-4 text-blue-700 font-bold">Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads to your users based on their visit to your sites and/or other sites on the Internet.</p>
    <h2 class="font-bold mt-4">3. Data Protection</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personally identifiable information to outside parties.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

